This is my new, I got this in the seatbelt.

42:34.094 --> 42:35.155
This is a Contax.

42:35.615 --> 42:38.438
This is a new state-of-the-art little miniature camera.

42:38.518 --> 42:39.699
This is all professional quality.

42:40.460 --> 42:44.484
This is the person who's at in the background.

42:44.504 --> 42:44.904
That's nice.

