Would you like me to send you any copies of these, if you'd like?

43:09.370 --> 43:11.072
Yes, I would.

43:11.305 --> 43:14.409
And great luck, my dear, I thought, well, I mean, you don't need to.

43:14.490 --> 43:16.212
It's going to be a great success.

43:16.332 --> 43:19.016
Why don't you just write an address here, a P.O.

43:19.076 --> 43:19.857
box or something?

43:19.877 --> 43:22.661
Oh, I'll put my number of address.

