Absolutely.

44:17.140 --> 44:18.041
Just a question now.

44:18.061 --> 44:18.882
You're Baroness.

44:18.902 --> 44:21.004
You might take your quarters off.

44:21.024 --> 44:24.449
What is the proper way to address you formally?

44:24.469 --> 44:25.710
Lady or Baroness?

44:25.830 --> 44:26.131
Oh, yes.

44:26.151 --> 44:27.112
Either is all right.

44:27.292 --> 44:28.073
Either is all right.

44:28.441 --> 44:30.803
Baroness James or Lady James doesn't matter.

44:30.823 --> 44:32.906
It doesn't really matter at all.

44:32.926 --> 44:36.149
Some baronesses, just like the baroness, could be Lady James.

44:36.169 --> 44:46.119
They could be the wife of a knight, the wife of a baron, the wife of a baroness, the wife of a baroness, the wife of a woman.

44:46.800 --> 44:50.323
There's an American woman married high to a married Viscount Eccles.

44:50.824 --> 44:51.865
Oh, yes, she's Viscountess.

44:51.885 --> 44:53.747
She's Viscountess or a lady.

